Place 1/2 cup frosting in a small bowl. Stir in red food coloring. Place remaining frosting in a small microwave-safe bowl. Microwave on high 8-10 second or until just melted; stir in green food coloring. Frost the center of each cookie with red frosting. Carefully spread edges with green frosting. Cut each cookie in half. Sprinkle each half with mini chocolate chips. Let set 10 minutes.